A RESOLUTION
1 Commending the men and women of the United States Armed Forces from the Greater
2 Augusta region; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the men and women of the United States Armed Forces have dedicated their
4 lives to the defense and protection of our nation, upholding the highest values of courage,
5 sacrifice, and service; and
6 WHEREAS, the Greater Augusta region is home to countless active-duty service members,
7 veterans, reservists, and National Guard personnel who have honorably served and continue
8 to serve in defense of our freedoms; and
9 WHEREAS, Fort Eisenhower (formerly Fort Gordon) and other military installations in the
10 region have played a critical role in national defense, providing strategic support, training,
11 and resources to ensure the readiness of our Armed Forces; and
12 WHEREAS, the families of our service members also bear the weight of sacrifice, providing
13 unwavering support and resilience as their loved ones answer the call of duty; and
