14 WHEREAS, the veterans of the Greater Augusta area have demonstrated extraordinary
15 bravery and dedication, transitioning from military service to continue contributing to the
16 community through leadership, public service, and economic development; and
17 WHEREAS, it is fitting and proper that we, as a community, express our profound gratitude
18 and appreciation for the selfless service, dedication, and valor exhibited by these
19 extraordinary men and women.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
21 commend the men and women of the United States Armed Forces from the Greater Augusta
22 region for their exemplary contributions to the security, prosperity, and well-being of our
23 great nation.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
25 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the public and the
26 press.
